nnoremap <C-f>      :set cursorline cursorcolumn<CR>/\V
nnoremap <C-h>      :TagbarOpen fjc<CR>
nnoremap <C-n>      gt
nnoremap <C-p>      gT
nnoremap <C-w>o     <C-w>o:redraw!<CR>
nnoremap <C-w>s     <C-w>s:redraw!<CR>
nnoremap <C-w>v     <C-w>v:redraw!<CR>
" }}}
